additionalProperty.value: Herb & parmesan chicken schnitzel (28%) (chicken, flour (wheat, maize), water, sunflower oil, canola oil, thickener (1404), salt,parmesan cheese powder (0.2%), wheat semolina, wheat gluten, polenta, herbs (0.1%), spices, dehydrated vegetables, wheatstarch, cheese powder, mineral salts (450, 451, 452, 500), egg powder, sugar, flavours (milk), acidity regulators (327, 270), yeastextracts, vegetable extracts, maltodextrin), potatoes (potatoes, canola oil), cheese sauce (19%) (water, cream (cream, thickener(401)), cheddar cheese, thickener (1422), flavours (dextrose (wheat), natural flavours (wheat, soy), wheat flour, spice extract(turmeric), natural colour (caramel i))), peas, carrots, butter sauce (butter, flavours (milk solids, wheat)).VEGETABLES (50%)

description: Juicy chicken schnitzel with a herb and Parmesan crumb, topped with a creamy white sauce and served with roast potatoes, carrots & green peas.
name: Red Box Plated Herb & Parmesan Chicken Schnitzel
